  "name": "RPlog_Bespin_Blows_Up",
  "title": "Disaster at the Bespin Miner's Dinner",
  "summary": "At the first annual Bespin Miner's Dinner in the Yarith Hotel ballroom on Cloud City, the harried Jedi manager Johanna te Danaan and her Zeltron friend Quinne Stardust Rose wrangle guests, a crude Gamorrean named Mox, and Johanna's foul-mouthed astromech Cricket, while the Falleen Lorda Nasiri arrives with undead neks and a cowled witch. The Caspian delegation of Moff Crestian Tarasar, the Wookiee Zaalbacca, and the Horansi diplomat Kasha mingles as foreman Orgrad Soval announces generous raises and worker shares to roaring applause. When Johanna is summoned to the refinery, catastrophe strikes: a massive explosion tears through the facility, Boba Fett blasts into the ballroom firing on the crowd, and Cloud City reels under a coordinated terrorist attack. With Johanna missing, Crestian assumes command and orders the system interdicted, while a panicked Quinne breaks down amid collapsing rigging and chaos.",
